<D>__{no..no..it's okay. it's me being bugged.}
<A>__{two people head for john almost simultaneously. peg, an arty looking woman in her late 50's..wild, scraggly gray hair, enters lugging an ice chest and the maitre d'.}
<C>__{peg}
<D>__{you are going to be so happy..}
