<A>__{he starts to prepare for cooking.}
<C>__{john }
<D>__{i worked in a kitchen once in new york that got four stars. it was like a line formed for the chance to become an asshole. people's accents changed. the heart went out of the place. you understand.}
<C>__{peter}
<D>__{no.}
